00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:38,000
 Because, like mentioned before in the testimony, the people we are serving in Branches of Hope

29
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:42,360
 have experienced the very opposite of what we're talking about, this love.

30
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:49,040
 They have experienced a brutality, most of them, that we can't even think or imagine.

31
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:53,920
 What is worse is that they are far away from the loving families that could be helping

32
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:57,040
 them heal from the traumas that they've experienced.

33
00:01:57,040 --> 00:02:02,160
 But I believe this community, you and I, God has placed us in this community to be that

