00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:23,600
 an allowance for utilities, we will hear more about it later, Lisa and James can now use

218
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:27,960
 their fan and have the lights on for longer.

219
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:33,120
 This has not only provided a more comfortable environment for them, you know the heat in

220
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:38,080
 Hong Kong, now they can turn their fan on.

221
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:41,960
 But it has given them a space for learning for James.

