00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:49,120
 So we're not only meeting the current needs, but we are speaking into destiny and the future.

223
00:15:49,120 --> 00:15:55,840
 Through the Road and Star Programs, our clients, they feel seen by us.

224
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:58,960
 They feel heard, that somebody cares.

225
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:01,540
 They feel cared for.

226
00:16:01,540 --> 00:16:03,460
 They feel comforted.

227
00:16:03,460 --> 00:16:05,320
 They feel covered.

228
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:07,600
 They feel hopeful.

229
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:10,680
